<link href="/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main class="container mx-auto p-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero h-64" style="background-image: url('/images/toronto-transit.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
        <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-60"></div>
        <div class="hero-content text-center text-white">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Public Transit in Toronto</h1>
            <p class="text-lg mt-2">Explore Toronto's convenient and reliable transit system.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Transit Details -->
    <section class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Toronto Transit Commission (TTC)</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <!-- Subways -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title text-xl font-semibold">Subways</h3>
                    <p>Toronto’s subway system is fast, reliable, and covers the city’s core. It’s the most efficient way to travel long distances quickly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Buses & Streetcars -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title text-xl font-semibold">Buses & Streetcars</h3>
                    <p>Buses and streetcars are ideal for shorter trips or areas not covered by the subway. They provide a great way to explore different neighborhoods in the city.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Transit Tips Section -->
    <section class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Transit Tips</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">To make your trip smoother, make sure to use a Presto card for easy payment on subways, buses, and streetcars.</p>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
